<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٩ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٧٤:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{فَأَمَّا الَّذِينَ شَقُوا فَفِي النَّارِ لَهُمْ فِيهَا زَفِيرٌ وَشَهِيقٌ}</span> <span class="c4">[هود: ١٠٦]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«زَفِيرٌ وَشَهِيقٌ شَدِيدٌ , وَصَوْتٌ ضَعِيفٌ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>